#originalTopic=does-intelligent-design-have-merit
"So we detect design by inferring that some parts appear to have been arranged for a purpose."Other inconvenient observations which bear inspection : purposefulness and intentionality. Here is that impermissible notion to the effect: "personality is void of material and therefore personality is not worthy of  notable consideration by   science  "Following that is dismissal and denial of  personal expressions and very often ad hominem character-assassination.We are forced to confront these challenges which in a more spiritual world might appear trivial or pathetic.  Be prepared which might advise be patient and have pity.